<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Skill-Gated Tasks & Internships</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 720px;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .features {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .features li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .actions a {
            flex: 1;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 12px 0;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: background 0.2s ease;
        }

        .actions a:hover {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #444;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Skill-Gated Tasks & Internships</h1>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Verified skills · Fixed-scope work · Academic-safe experience
        </p>

        <p class="description">
            A backend-first platform where students gain real-world experience
            through short-duration tasks and internships, accessible only after
            skill verification and monitored through admin-controlled workflows.
        </p>

        <ul class="features">
            <li>✔ Skill verification before task access</li>
            <li>✔ Fixed-duration, clearly scoped tasks</li>
            <li>✔ Admin-reviewed submissions and approvals</li>
            <li>✔ Academic workload protection enforced</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/auth/register/student">Register as Student</a>
            <a href="/auth/register/org">Register as Organization</a>
            <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Backend system built with Node.js, Express & MongoDB
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

